Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.84,1:21:04.27,main-cn,,0,0,0,,哥哥 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 1,1:21:02.84,1:21:04.27,main-jp,,0,0,0,,早うお帰りい
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.28,1:21:12.98,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}圣洁的微光把我们包围
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.28,1:21:12.98,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}seems to hallow us there,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.40,1:21:21.59,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Which, seek thro' the world
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.40,1:21:21.59,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}这一切的一切 哪怕走遍天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.96,1:21:30.91,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}也无处寻觅
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.96,1:21:30.91,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}is ne'er met with elsewhere
