Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.48,1:21:51.15,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}sweet
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.84,1:21:59.95,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}又美好的家
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.84,1:21:59.95,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}sweet home
